org.azeckoski.reflectutils.map
Class ArrayOrderedMap<K,V>

java.lang.Object
  java.util.AbstractMap<K,V>
      java.util.HashMap<K,V>
          org.azeckoski.reflectutils.map.ArrayOrderedMap<K,V>
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Cloneable, Map<K,V>, OrderedMap<K,V>
public class ArrayOrderedMap<K,V>
extends HashMap<K,V>
implements OrderedMap<K,V>

A map which keeps track of the order the entries are added and allows retrieval of entries in the order they were entered as well, this is NOT safe for multi-threaded access, this is backed by a HashMap and ArrayList

Author:
Aaron Zeckoski (azeckoski @ gmail.com)
